(1, 'Graphic Designing', 'graphic-designing', '<p class=\"text-center\"><em>More than a poodle, don&rsquo;t mistake it for a doodle. Graphic designing is demanding yet rewarding. Multi-purpose in its pursuits, it is an amalgamation of written and visual content.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Graphic designing is a skill that judiciously combines texts and pictures and produces a unique image that can be used for various purposes, like, creating posters, flyers, brochures etc. or as logo, for various brands. It takes several technical parts like graphic tools, design definitions, fundamental design concepts etc. to build a brand portfolio.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Graphic Designing might look like a fun job doodling pictures, but it is, in fact, a very demanding task. Every little component has to be just right to produce a striking effigy. Graphic designing is composed of various steps, which soups up your complete brand portfolio. These steps are:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Logo Designing</strong>: In this a logo is designed, keeping in mind your company&rsquo;s name and nature of work.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Typography</strong>: The text is calibrated by deciding upon, the font size and choosing from various fonts available, or even drawing it manually.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Selection of Colour</strong>: Next comes the selection of a colour theme according to the nature of your work and setting it along with the logo to give it definition.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Application of Brand</strong>: Once the brand portfolio gets ready, it is launched as marketing collateral and its popularity is closely observed and analyzed. Once it gets accepted by audience, marketing strategies for the product and services are built around the graphic theme of the brand.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Doors Studio, we offer coolest graphics for your brand to stand out from the crowd of billions. We have in our team, professionally trained but passion-driven skilled graphic designers who craft quirky, yet novel graphics that can endow your brand with an eye-catching image. The illustrations we provide can take your brand marketing campaigns to unfathomed heights.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Doors Studio - India &amp; UAE Presence</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a leading Logo &amp; graphics designs Agency in Delhi,India our clientele is spread across India &amp; UAE. You can now avail our best <a href=\"graphic-logo-designing-in-uae-abudhabi-ras-al-khaimah-dubai-sharjah.php\">logo designs &amp; graphics design services in Abudhabi, RAS-Al-kaimah, Dubai, Sharjah and UAE</a></p>', 'Graphic Designing', 'CREATIVE LOGO DESIGNING AGENCY & GRAPHIC DESIGNING COMPANY IN DELHI & GOA', 'GET YOU GRAPHIC DESIGNING & LOGO DESIGNING DONE BY THE LEADERS IN GOA & DELHI', 'Logo Designing Company, Graphic Designing Agency in Delhi, Goa - Doors Studio', 'Graphic Designing Company, Logo Designing Agency - Doors Studio is a leader in creative graphic designing and logo designing services in Delhi and Goa that caters super class designs for your website.', 'graphic design company, logo design company, graphic design company in India', '5eaac2ba09c5bgraphics-image.jpg', '2020-01-07 13:16:21', '2020-04-30 07:23:46'),
(2, 'UI & UX Design', 'web-design', '<p>Did you know that it takes just about 50 milliseconds (1 second) for visitors to make up their mind about how good a site is? Just by looking at the design of your website they can figure out whether the site is professional and trustworthy or not. Our professional website design company team is ready to help you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>WHAT IS</strong> WEBSITE DESIGN?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Design is when you design the website according to your liking and restructure it in the best possible way. Website Design involves a process of organization, innovation and upgrade of websites. Website Design even includes features like information architecture, website structure, user interface, navigation ergonomics, website plan, colors, contrasts, fonts, images as well as designing of icons.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>WHEN DO YOU </strong> NEED TO DESIGN YOUR WEBSITE?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The reasons for getting a new design for your website are when:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>You are not achieving the results targeted by you</li>\r\n	<li>When the purpose of your company changes</li>\r\n	<li>Your Website stops being responsive</li>\r\n	<li>You want to include an improved content strategy</li>\r\n	<li>To outrun competitors in the market.</li>\r\n	<li>Upgrading your website according to the au courant market trend.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>HOW TO MAKE THE BEST </strong> DESIGN FOR A WEBSITE?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For you to design a website which is attractive, you need to be updating yourself with recent developments regarding the techniques of web designing. A clean design, Responsive site, font size, and simple navigation tools are some of the factors that go in to creating the best design for any website. Doors Studio helps create the design for such websites.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"customhdquality\"> <img src=\"https://www.doorsstudio.com/images/moniter.png\" alt=\"website design services\">\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"highlighter\">\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"highlight1\"><span><strong>HD Quality</strong> Web design</span></div>\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"highlight2\"><span>modern, high-definition</span></div>\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"highlight1\"><span>We never use templates</span></div>\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"highlight2\"><span>100% Custom</span></div>\r\n\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>FACTORS THAT CONTRIBUTE</strong> TO WEB DESIGN</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Layout</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The layout of a webpage is a significant aspect of web design. It speaks about the manner in which the graphics, ads and text are arranged. This enhances the overall visual appearance of a website and contributes to its design aspect. The balance and aesthetic content of a page is integral to a webpage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The palette of colors used on a webpage depends upon the purpose and the customer preference of the website. It could range from a monochrome look to an entirely colorful background, depending upon the requirement of the brand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fonts</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fonts have the capability of uplifting the design of a website. A lot depends on the kind of font you are using for your website content. Most of the web developers prefer using &ldquo;web safe fonts&rdquo; since web browsers only read specific kinds of fonts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Content</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When they say &ldquo;Content is King&rdquo;, it is true. Good and useful content is an important element while making of a website. A suitable design and informative content play a vital role in shaping your website to a large extent. Your SEO will also hugely rely on the kind of content you are posting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Graphics</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Graphics comprise of logos, photos, clipart or icons. These features add to the attractiveness of the webpage. For making the website user friendly these elements need to be placed in accordance with the color and the content. A well planned website attracts maximum users to click on your website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Doors Studio - India &amp; UAE Presence</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a leading UI Design / UX Design &amp; development Agency in Delhi, India our clientele is spread across India &amp; UAE. You can now avail our best <a href=\"website-ui-ux-designing-in-uae-abudhabi-ras-al-khaimah-dubai-sharjah.php\">UI / UX designing &amp; development company in Abudhabi, RAS-Al-kaimah, Dubai, Sharjah and UAE</a></p>', 'PROFESSIONAL UI & UX DESIGN SERVICES', 'A CREATIVE UI DESIGN, UX DESIGN & DEVELOPMENT AGENCY IN DELHI & GOA', 'WEBSITE DESIGN THAT STANDS OUT', 'UI Design, UX Design & Development in Delhi, Goa | India - Doors Studio', 'UI Design / UX Design & Development Agency - Doors Studio is a leading India\'s top website designs like UI Design, UX Design & Development agency in Delhi and Goa that offers responsive design, custom designs services for your website.', 'website Design Services Company, responsive website design, custom web designs services', '5eaac46b6a25bdesign-image.jpg', '2020-03-02 06:26:16', '2020-04-30 09:02:38'),
(3, 'Packaging Design', 'packaging-design', '<p>Acting like a cherry on the top, packing design is a branding tool which you directly hand out on the shelves and in general, in the lives of your consumer. The identity is associated with it which creates a brand recall due to specific colour, font and design which you use in it.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The kind of branding you do through packaging can play a very important role. It is imperative that you are clear with the idea and purpose of designing the package because a bad one can leave a long-lasting impact on the customer&rsquo;s mind.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To your surprise, Graphic Packaging has an International philosophy which gave birth to <strong>&ldquo;Three P&#39;s&rdquo;</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>● <strong>Protection</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The packaging should be sturdy enough to keep the product from the time of packing until it is delivered. As per your product, the material used it selected which then goes into major manufacturing for mass supply&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>● <strong>Preservation</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This point is very important from the perspective of a food brand because if it is spoiled inside the packaging itself, that leaves a very negative impact on the consumer, which may lead to people switching to a different brand.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>● <strong>Promotion</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is the part where you decide what your product will convey to the consumer who will be holding it in their hand. Here we decide:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>❖ Brand Content - Tagline, Phrase or Qualities</p>\r\n\r\n<p>❖ Colour and Font of the brand</p>\r\n\r\n<p>❖ Guidelines - MFG date, how to use, how to store and so on</p>', 'Packaging Design', 'Packaging Design', NULL, 'Packaging Design', 'Packaging Design', NULL, '1583131430.jpg', '2020-03-02 06:43:50', '2020-03-02 06:43:50'),
(4, 'Branding', 'branding', '<p>Branding as a tool is like defining the personality of your brand through a visual and written medium which in whole builds your brand identity in the market. There will be several clothing labels or shoe brand, but how they position themselves in the market separates each of them, helping the consumer to identify and recall.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Branding has several steps, it is just not mere colour, words or font.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Strategy&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A concept is first given birth to build a fort of your strategy. What will be your brand&rsquo;s strong suit over which your marketing activities will be made, is the question you ask while sitting down to formulate a strategy. Here you:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>● <strong>Identify the USPs of your brand</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>● <strong>In-depth and unique insights for brand integration</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>● <strong>Colour, font and design (like logo design)</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Identify&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>While making the strategy, we decide the market we will be targeting for a particular brand as per the demographics. This helps in deciding what content needs to create as per the demographics.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Brand Integration&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Here the two-level integration work:&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>● <strong>The special insights are combined with the facts and figure to make them interesting and pleasing.&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>●<strong>&nbsp;Design content for the brand that is relevant to the incoming trends and festivities.</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Consistency and Design&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here you combine the creatives with a plan of action and start marketing your content on the digital platforms.</p>', 'Branding', 'Branding', NULL, 'Branding', 'Branding', NULL, '1583131762.jpg', '2020-03-02 06:49:22', '2020-03-02 06:49:22'),
(5, 'Web Development', 'web-development', '<p class=\"text-center\"><em>Not boulders or bricks but codes and wits, a lot goes into creating your space on the world wide web. We know it is close to your heart. </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>What is </strong> Web Development?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Development is the work that goes into building, creating and maintenance of a website on the internet as well as the intranet (personal network). Development of web ranges from development of a single stationary page to complicated web based internet applications, E-Business as well as social networking services. Currently, Web development also refers to the making of Content Management Systems (CMS). Web design, Web publishing, Web programming, and database management are some of the significant features within the ambit of Web Development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Difference between </strong> Web Design and Development</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web Design is the division that is associated to the first look of the site, and what your prospective buyer will witness when they visit your webpage. Web Development is inclusive of the programming that would eventually take place on the webpage. This even incorporates the systematic arrangement of the pages, applications and functions which will make your website work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>When should </strong> Web Development ideally begin?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When it comes to developing a website, the procedure will begin as soon as the design of the website has been finalized. Once that happens, the web developers will start organizing the coding and retaining similar designs for rest of the webpage&rsquo;s.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This can alter according to the priority of the project. For instance, the main point here should not to be the beauty or the layout, but the fine working of the system, so that web development can begin as soon as possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>FACTS YOU NEED TO KNOW ABOUT WEB DEVELOPMENT</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Websites have always undergone a lot of changes with time. In order to be updated with the happenings in the digital world an update on the latest coding standards, browser capability updates and search engine algorithms is extremely important.</li>\r\n	<li>Your website should look amazing and be functional on all mediums, whether it is a browser or an iphone. A Browser Capability Testing helps you recognize possible problems and fixes them immediately.</li>\r\n	<li>Website coding is an important aspect when you are looking at Development of a website. The manner in which your website will be coded will directly impact your search engine listings. A well coded website is the core to a well functional website. When you implicate clean practices, it adds to your website standing according to search engines.</li>\r\n	<li>Great Images and video can enhance the look and design of your website. A website with attractive multimedia content attracts visitors to your website. But if not used properly it can also impact the overall performance of your website. Using optimized images for videos and images by web developers increases the visitor engagement on your website.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Doors Studio - India &amp; UAE Presence</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a leading website development company in Delhi, India our clientele is spread across India &amp; UAE. You can now avail our best <a href=\"website-development-in-uae-abudhabi-ras-al-khaimah-dubai-sharjah.php\">website development company in Abudhabi, RAS-Al-kaimah, Dubai, Sharjah and UAE</a></p>', 'WEB DEVELOPMENT SERVICES', 'WEBSITE DESIGNING & WEBSITE DEVELOPMENT COMPANY IN DELHI & GOA', 'CUSTOM WEB DEVELOPMENT SERVICES COMPANY | INDIA', 'Website Development Company, Website Designing in Delhi, Goa- Doors Studio', 'Website Designing, Website Development Company - Doors Studio is a India’s top agency for Website Designing ,Website Development services that offers best custom designing and development services  for your business website.', 'web development company in India, Web Development Services in Delhi, Web Development Services in India, Web Development Services Company', '5eaac87f17097development-image.jpg', '2020-03-02 06:53:59', '2020-04-30 07:24:49'),
(6, 'Web Application Development', 'web-application-development', '<p>Online Application development is the sole cause of such a boom in technology that we have witnessed in the past few years. It&#39;s a blend of programming languages working in sync in order to bring the website alive. Without the growth and advancement of web application nothing, you see online today would ever have existed. Google, Amazon, Facebook, eBay, Alibaba, Flipkart, and many others rely on the online application to make their companies successful.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Development:</strong> Using the design, the programmers use that as the basis of building a structure with the codes and algorithms to give life to the design envisioned.</p>', 'Web Application Development', 'Web Application Development', NULL, 'Web Application Development', 'Web Application Development', NULL, '1583132395.jpg', '2020-03-02 06:59:55', '2020-03-02 01:30:48'),
(7, 'E-Commerce Development', 'e-commerce-development', '<p class=\"text-center\"><em>Why a busy street or an air-conditioned floor when you can access your shop with Netflix on. (In the other window, of course). </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Online stores or e-commerce are like an engine that makes the Internet more accessible. Without its help 80% of the online based companies that exist today would never have functioned. E commerce is the next level platform for the setting up of any kind of business online as these online stores act as a catalyst in widening the reach of your product, services or business. A stunning E- commerce design gives you an edge over your online competitors and makes you more visible to the users that you are looking forward to target.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>What&#39;s available on</strong> an online store?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>An <strong>online e-commerce site</strong> is not merely a website that trades its goods and services, but is a one stop shop that manages all your online transactions. If you are in a search for a platform to introduce your business into the international market, then you will definitely be requiring someone with innovative ideas and expertise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>What do we</strong> deliver?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Doors Studio has an in-depth knowledge and expertise that will assist you in building a world class online store which will not only appear aesthetically pleasing and works efficiently, but will also prove to be an asset for your company for inviting new customers and will further help you in building upon your current client base.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Doors Studio is a One Stop Solutions Company dedicated in providing our users with detailed knowledge and the capabilities required in the current online scenario, that will prove to be the topmost options for them to tap maximum returns from their online ventures. We do not believe in working with accordance to pre existing themes, or pre-built websites, and we do not recommend our clients to use software easily available online. At Doors Studio we have created a customized system that functions in accordance with your needs, preference <strong>features you decide to include</strong> in order to run your very <strong>own successful online business</strong>. We make sure that we come up with an interesting and engaging website that in the coming years will enhance and maintain your online reputation in every aspect possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How do you maintain your</strong> visitor loyalty?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Online Visitors mainly purchase from the vendors they trust. With this predominant idea, you will give in your best to showcase your website as the best among the others. Having a unique design along with a functional and convenient shopping cart that promotes a fun filled shopping experience will make all the difference for you!. While most online businesses today start with a separate e-commerce website, with Doors Studio you can easily add an E-commerce solution to your website. Doors Studio just makes it easier for you!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Can you transform</strong> my website into an e-commerce online store?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have a site that produces quality, converting it into an <strong>e-commerce online store</strong> can transform it merely in to a money minting machine. There are a variety of choices available which can be used by you in <strong>deciding how to transform your website</strong> into a successful e-commerce online store. While looking out for a company to make or transform your current website into a successful e commerce online store you should also exercise necessary caution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How can I be sure I&#39;m going</strong> to like what you created for me?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All our designs are 100% guaranteed. This means that if you are not entirely contented with our design initially we will consistently work towards in ensuring that you will <strong>ABSOLUTELY SATISFIED</strong>! with our services. The most important point you should keep in mind while starting your own online business is that; An E-commerce website <strong>requires massive investment</strong>. There will be a return to your investment, once you make smart choices in the right direction.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Still not sure</strong> if E-Commerce website design &amp; development is what you&#39;re searching for?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you&#39;re looking forward to upgrade your current eCommerce website or you want to start accepting payments online, Doors Studio is the right choice for you for getting in to the online e commerce bandwagon.</p>', 'E-COMMERCE WEBSITE DESIGN & DEVELOPMENT SERVICES', 'STRATEGIC ECOMMERCE WEBSITE DESIGNING & DEVELOPMENT COMPANY IN DELHI & GOA', 'RESPONSIVE E-COMMERCE WEBSITE DESIGN THAT WORKS AS A CONVERSION ENGINE!', 'Ecommerce Website Designing & Development Company in Goa, Delhi - Doors Studio', 'Ecommerce Website Designing & Development Company - Doors Studio is a well-known for developing high quality responsive designs for ecommerce website in PHP, Laravel, Codeigniter, MVC framework etc.', 'E-Commerce website design, E-Commerce website development, E-Commerce magento development in India', '5eaacd0494d4cecommerce-image.jpg', '2020-03-02 07:02:50', '2020-04-30 07:35:08'),
(8, 'API Integration', 'api-integration', '<p class=\"text-center\"><em>Turning you limitless </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>What is</strong> API Integration development?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>API is also known as Application Programming Interface and it described as the procedures that permit one application to connect along with other programs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also, the API is a language that permits one program to transfer information to another program, ensuring that they both identify each other. Applying the API, your website or application &#39;gains&#39; all the information that will available to you via the API programs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Who uses</strong> API Integration?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The API is widely applied by all the major companies worldwide as the API is a program that allows them to update and sync the current functionalities with their own choices. APIs are becoming increasingly popular since major companies now have their own API which allows you to easily access their data.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>When do I require</strong> an API Integration?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>API is highly efficient and is primarily used for the purpose of online applications and sites. The API works by granting its visitors and customers an opportunity to access the required data available on a particular site. Such a program makes your website more easily assessable and assists in joining with the other programs and giving or requesting information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For instance, when you use your Twitter account to register on any other site. The set up that assists in connecting both the sites is called the API. Yet another illustration for this is when a online cart provides you with the shipping price of a company. The API&#39;s allows you to conveniently publish the shipping company details on the shopping cart website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How long</strong> does it take for API integration?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The time taken for integrating the API varies depending upon how complicated the API is. Most of the APIs come with the required information for you to work on. In other instances an API is just a specification of remote calls.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>How do I know</strong> that I need an API Software to be integrated?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are want to create a program that will act as a link between two or more programs exchanging information or data between each other, then you will be requiting an API. You can interact with one of our many API Integrations specialists and learn more as to which kind of an API is suitable to your need and requirement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Stay ahead in your business</strong> with the best API integration services</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>API has knowingly or unknowingly become a major part of our day to day lives with the digitalization of the current era. Now more and more people are signing into apps as well as websites using their previously used API, and this has enhanced the convenience as well as the security concerns. This has lead to the hike in demand for the API developers in the market. The competition is stiff, so you should know the nuts and bolts of API to find a developer who can marvelously develop the API for your app or website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>A brief profile of <strong>API Integration Development</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>API that is an abbreviation for Application Programming Interface that is essentially a set of procedures and functions allowing the creation of applications that access the features is data of a standard operating system, application or another service. The API elementarily works by granting visitors the access to the required data available on a particular site. So the program helps you in making the entire registering process convenient for the users. There are numerous benefits of API integration Development. Some of these are:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Minimizing errors and data duplicity issues for your website or app.</li>\r\n	<li>Saving valuable time and resources.</li>\r\n	<li>Enable the data-driven decisions.</li>\r\n	<li>Deliver flexible creativity.</li>\r\n	<li>Integrates the application network.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sometimes the entire API integration development process can be quite complicated while sometimes the entire task falls like a breeze so what amount of time would be required for the entire process depends on the website framework as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Get the <strong>service accessibility</strong> almost everywhere</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No matter where you have the headquarters of your business, a profound online presence can reach millions of customers across the globe in a matter of seconds. This is certainly one of the most important things you need in your business regardless of anything else. Services from a good API integration development company like Doors Studio can help you in making your products and services accessible to your customers whenever they want to.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you have API integration development services for your e-commerce business with Doors Studio, you do not have to be online all the time to monitor your business proceedings because the framework will help you convey the messages to the ideal customers accordingly. The online websites help your customers to buy anything they want at any time of the hour without any problem.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Wrapping up</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you are building an e-commerce business, security and accessibility should also be on your priority list. Once you have created an e-commerce website, it can help you change the contents whenever you need to. With Doors Studio, you can rest assured because the API framework is 100% secure for business use and also gives you higher scalability. You can get the services for both big and small businesses without wasting much time and energy. Plus our services come in a price that won&rsquo;t burn a hole in your pocket. So what are you waiting for?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Doors Studio - India &amp; UAE Presence</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a leading API Integration Agency in Delhi,India our clientele is spread across India &amp; UAE. You can now avail our top notch <a href=\"api-integration-in-uae-abudhabi-ras-al-khaimah-dubai-sharjah.php\">API Integration services in Abudhabi, RAS-Al-kaimah, Dubai, Sharjah and UAE.</a></p>', 'THIRD PARTY API INTEGRATION SERVICE', 'HELPING WEBSITES IN THIRD PARTY API INTEGRATION ACROSS MULTIPLE PLATFORMS IN INDIA', 'INDIA\'S BEST THIRD PARTY API INTEGRATION SERVICE PROVIDER', '3rd Party API Integration & Development Service in Delhi, Goa, India - Doors Studio', 'Third Party API Integration Development Service Company / Agency - Doors Studio is a leading Delhi based third party API Integration development company / agency. We develop and Integrate Custom API. Also do Custom Business to Business API integration.', 'Third Party API Integration Company / Agency in Delhi, Goa, India - Doors Studio is a leading Delhi based API Integration development company / agency that offer to develop and Integrate Custom API Integration services and Also do Custom Business to Business API integration.', '5eaad374be48bapi-image.jpg', '2020-03-02 07:04:37', '2020-04-30 08:02:36'),
(9, 'Mobile Application Development', 'mobile-applications', '<p class=\"text-center\"><em>Your next step, carefully crafted by us. </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As the technology has developed, it has given whole new realm to the use of internet. Before smart phones came, people wanted laptops more than desktops, but now, ever since the arrival of smart phones and tablets, people feel more comfortable using these more than their laptops. This has resulted in drifting of the website user traffic to the easy-going mobile apps, in accordance with the <strong>Law of Accessibility</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mobile apps add a completely fresh dimension to your marketing strategy by enhancing the user experience. They provide services similar to PC, except that they can be used on the go. In the fast paced corporate setting, they have made users&rsquo; lives easier and more dynamic. Most companies are now-a-days choosing mobile apps to reach millions of smart phone and tablet using customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mobile apps are economical for users in terms of time and internet data cost, especially for the websites that need a lot of per day time to browse. Most of these websites are included in the following categories:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Mobile Application for E-commerce Websites</strong>: Usually these websites have huge online stores and take up too much time to go through all the available products before finally settling for something to buy. Examples of such websites are Jabong, Flipkart, Amazon, Snapdeal, Homeshop18 and many more.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Mobile Application for Social Media Websites</strong>: These websites generally need to be visited many times every day, and opening them is such an easy affair when it is done using mobile apps, as opposed to using them on PC. A few examples of these websites are Facebook, Instagram, Pinterest, Twitter, etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mobile apps allow users to look up their favorite products on various shopping websites while they are on breaks from work, or studies; and check out their social media accounts every time a notification buzzes in, multiple times a day. So, with mobile apps make their lives easier, as in they don&rsquo;t need to waste time and effort in switching on a PC every time they want to skim through their Facebook or Twitter account.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mobile Apps created by Doors studio are so noticeable that it allows your customers to sift through various products and services offered in no time with easy selection process for buying what they like. Instead of going through all the windows in a PC, customers can avail your products at one platform, and pay for it effortlessly. This not only boosts your direct sales, but also acts as a competent marketing tool for your company through ratings and comments left by the consumers. It helps in developing Brand Loyalty as well. Moreover, you can also give ads of your app on websites or on other apps which ultimately helps you boost your sales.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Doors Studio - India &amp; UAE Presence</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a leading mobile applications development company in Delhi, India our clientele is spread across India &amp; UAE. You can now avail our top notch <a href=\"mobile-application-development-in-uae-abudhabi-ras-al-khaimah-dubai-sharjah.php\">mobile application development services in Abudhabi, RAS-Al-kaimah, Dubai, Sharjah and UAE</a></p>', 'MOBILE APPS DEVELOPMENT', 'ANDROID MOBILE & IOS APP DEVELOPMENT - MOBILE APPLICATION DEVELOPMENT COMPANY IN DELHI & GOA', 'DOORS STUDIO IS A INDIA\'S TOP MOBILE APPS DEVELOPMENT SERVICES COMPANY', 'Mobile Application Development Company in Delhi & Goa - Android & iOS App Development', 'Mobile Application, Android Apps, iOS Development Company / Agency – Doors Studio is a leading mobile application development company like Android app development, iphone apps development, iOS Apps development in Delhi, India. We develop the most up-to-date mobile apps development for your Business.', 'Mobile Apps Development Company, Top Mobile Application Development Company, Mobile Apps Development Company in India', '5eaad1423561cmobile-apps-image.jpg', '2020-03-02 07:06:18', '2020-04-30 07:53:14'),
(10, 'CRM & ERP', 'crm-erp', '<p><strong>CRM</strong> greatly and efficiently help companies in the management of current &amp; potential customers. It is nothing but a software which aid in organizing, automating and synchronizing services like sales, marketing &amp; customer service.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ERP</strong> enables businesses in management, just like CRM helps you manage the customers. Its sole purpose is to improve the efficiency of the business processes. Employees are assigned and monitored through this software to assess their growth and productivity. Also, any inefficiency or issues can be easily figured out in this and resolved by taking immediate action.</p>', 'CRM & ERP', 'CRM & ERP', NULL, 'CRM & ERP', 'CRM & ERP', NULL, '1583132904.jpg', '2020-03-02 07:08:24', '2020-03-02 07:08:24'),
(11, 'Blog Content', 'blog-content', '<p>Blogging is initially termed as Weblogs which act like online journals and allow a brand to give a daily update about the new developments which are in a byte size information format. But with SEO in the picture, the information widened and now blogs are more than just byte size information and allow brands to not just use them to make their consumer engaged and aware, but also to use it as a marketing tool. Now blogging has several types:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>● <strong>PR article</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Press releases are like statements about or from the brand which generally includes industry insights and new developments of the brand.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>● <strong>Newsletter Writing</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A brand can choose to have their own newsletter which can be used as a newspaper specific to the company having information about the insights, achievements and people of the company.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>● <strong>Article Writing</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This form of blog writing includes articles which are meant for publishing on offline and online portals where the brand endorses itself.</p>', 'Blog Content', 'Blog Content', NULL, 'Blog Content', 'Blog Content', NULL, '1583133131.jpg', '2020-03-02 07:12:11', '2020-03-02 07:12:11'),
(12, 'Search Engine Optimization', 'search-engine-optimization', '<p class=\"text-center\"><em>They don&rsquo;t Google just to Google. </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.doorsstudio.com/images/seo-page.jpg\" style=\"width:100%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Need to know - Tactics of New SEO Services vs Old SEO Services</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SEO is the procedure through which the written part of your website is redesigned for facilitating communication between the data present on your website and the search tools. In On Page SEO - Code, Internal links to the page, All meta data, Alt tag with images and the outline all play a massive role on how your website is received by all the search platforms. The more popular or simpler long tail keywords you have put on your site, the more beneficial it is for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Tactics you can use to improve your SEO Ranking</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Choosing the right keywords</li>\r\n	<li>Choosing keywords or phrases that are more relevant</li>\r\n	<li>Regular Content Upgrade</li>\r\n	<li>Publish content that are relevant to the primary keywords</li>\r\n	<li>Focus on creating strong inter links within the text on your website</li>\r\n	<li>Put alt tags below your video or image content.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Changing Face of SEO</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Putting the right Keywords was thought to be the right approach towards SEO building. It is believed that incorporating a lot of keywords helps build the SEO of your website. What actually happening is that search engines are recognizing this keyword adding approach as &ldquo;Keyword stuffing&rdquo;.<br />\r\nWhen this starts happening, the search engines start identifying you as a spammer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For fixing this recurring problem, instead of stuffing keywords you should include the keywords in a natural way. The required keywords should flow in your writing, in such a way that it looks organic. And not forced.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you write a blog for your website your main focus should be on &ldquo;what matters to your readers&rdquo; rather than just including keywords or phrases between the lines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>How can my website be visible on Major Search Engines?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How can you make your site stand apart from the other competitive players? How can you get maximum visits without cashing out a penny on promotions or campaigns? Search Engine Optimization (SEO) will do this for you. Our Indian Search Engine Optimization Company can help your website get one of the top rankings on various search engines. When a visitor searches for something specific on the search engine the term is also known as a keyword. The aim of a SEO is to optimize your site in such a manner that all the content posted on your site is relevant to all of the search engines, with special focus on keywords.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Doors Studio can aid you to augment the position of your website and make it one among the most searched for website in its respective field.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With our awesome SEO plan we can assist you to upgrade your ranking level on the topmost search engines, such as Google Chrome, Internet Explorer and Bing amongst others. SEO is essential for any kind of business to exist in the highly competitive online scenario of today.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What is the right time to start SEO for a new website?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The apt time to begin a (Search Engine Optimization) SEO is right at the launching period. Once your website has been launched Google crawls your website resulting in to getting the first placement. Another right time to get begin is as soon as possible!.The most interesting part about strategy is that your website will start with a strong ranking right at its beginning of its formation, but this will not be the deciding factor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Wait a second - Why Your SEO Rankings dropped and What to Do About It?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the benefits of having a SEO specialist with you is that they know what works, what doesn&#39;t and what can be done to help you get more visibility on the web. Sometimes being on the top of the 2nd page is better than being on the bottom of the 1st page. By the time they get to the base of the first webpage, your page visitor is bored of watching at results that are not relevant to him, so what will he do? He goes to the second or third page and tries again as a result. And who&#39;s on that second page? Why, it&#39;s your site! Exactly! where you want it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We all most probably known what SEO is, but what exactly does Search Engine Optimization stand for? SEO, simply put are tools and techniques that assist in getting your website top ranking during organic search results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SEO has the capability of making your website more visible to the person who searches for brands, products or services through search engines like Yahoo, Google or Bing. Title tags, keywords, image tags, internal link structure, and inbound links are some of the few tools and techniques that if used strategically can boost your website SEO, but these are just some of them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But apart from these factors, there are other factors as well that influence the SEO of a website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The design, structure and behavioral patterns of the website are essential factors, while working on the SEO of a website in an overall manner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>How can SEO help you?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>86% of online users feel that that using a search engine permits them to discover something new or important each day, thereby increasing their knowledge. It is said that Businesses that have websites comprising of 401-1000 pages attract 6x more leads than websites having 51-100 pages.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gone are the days of advertising in Yellow Pages and Magazines was a norm, since SEO generates more business referrals than any Yellow Page Advertising.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Currently Search Engines are used by people to search for products or services they are searching for. For this, they fill the appropriate keywords in to search engines like Bing, Yahoo or You Tube. On doing this, the search engines display sites based on ranking and authority.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Doors Studio we help your website get ranked at the top of the search engine hierarchy. This increases the chances of people clicking and visiting your website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Doors Studio - India &amp; UAE Presence</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a leading SEO Agency in Delhi,India our clientele is spread across India &amp; UAE. You can now avail our best <a href=\"ppc-seo-agency-company-in-uae-abudhabi-ras-al-khaimah-dubai-sharjah.php\">SEO agency in Abudhabi, RAS-Al-kaimah, Dubai, Sharjah and UAE</a></p>', 'SEO SERVICES', 'A COMPLETE RANGE OF SEO SERVICES FROM THE TOP SEO COMPANY IN DELHI', 'OUR SEO SERVICES HELP BOOST YOUR WEBSITE\'S \"RANKINGS\", \"NATURAL TRAFFIC\", WEBSITE ROI\" ETC.', 'SEO Company in Delhi, SEO Services in Delhi, SEO Agency Delhi - Doors Studio', 'SEO Company in Delhi, India - Doors Studio is leading high rated SEO company in Delhi that offers best SEO services for your website which helps to increase organic traffic, online visibility and maximize your business ROI.', 'seo company india, seo services, seo services india, seo company in delhi', '5eaad88c61017seo-image.jpg', '2020-03-02 07:15:47', '2020-04-30 08:27:12'),
(13, 'Copywriting', 'copywriting', '<p>It is well said that what you can say with one line sometimes even a thousand words fail to describe. Copyrighting is that sword that cuts into the mind of people with just one sharp and swift line. It helps to build an instant connection as the attention span is less over social media. It says in the mind of people way longer than any article. This can be used as a brand recall weapon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The difference between content writing and copywriting is that content writing is heavy on information which is explained in more than just one line and copywriting is mostly publicity and advertisement content which needs to short, crisp and hard-hitting.</p>', 'Copywriting', 'Copywriting', NULL, 'Copywriting', 'Copywriting', NULL, '1583133655.jpg', '2020-03-02 07:20:55', '2020-03-02 07:20:55'),
(14, 'Website Content', 'website-content', '<p>Website content is your brand biography where you can explain about the brand&rsquo;s inception, objective and products which they deal in. Here we set a tone when comes to brand language, whether it be professional or quirky, depending upon your industry and dynamics.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is an important part of setting the standard of your website which is decided by the number of visitors. If it is not creative, the chances are it might not interest the reader. This also includes featuring your PR articles, copywriting, blogging of various kinds and one binding force, which is dynamic and witty content.</p>', 'Website Content', 'Website Content', NULL, 'Website Content', 'Website Content', NULL, '1583134431.jpg', '2020-03-02 07:33:51', '2020-03-02 07:33:51'),
(15, 'Video Content', 'video-content', '<p>Video content helps in directing your brand&rsquo;s vision through a lens. But it is just not a moving picture. It involves ideating a concept that is unique yet relevant to your brand. That concept needs to be target audience-friendly, should advertise your brand directly or indirectly and it would be the icing on the cake if it involves a message that moves the audience.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video content is very pivotal as it helps the audience to engage with your brand with all their senses and create a deeper bond. It boosts the recollection rate and interactive nature leaves the audience with visual satisfaction.</p>', 'Video Content', 'Video Content', NULL, 'Video Content', 'Video Content', NULL, '1583134520.jpg', '2020-03-02 07:35:20', '2020-03-02 07:35:20');
INSERT INTO `services` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `post`, `banner_heading`, `h1`, `h2`, `meta_title`, `meta_description`, `meta_keyword`, `header_img`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(16, 'Digital Marketing', 'digital-marketing', '<p class=\"text-center\"><em>Being Here Matters! </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The ABC of digital marketing starts from the fundamental necessity of all the companies to get their products/services noticed by the prospective buyers. Various types of marketing activities are broadly kept under into two heads: <strong>internet channels and non-internet channels</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. Internet Marketing Channels: that need internet for the transmission of information:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Search Engine Marketing (SEM)</strong>:SEM mainly thrives on paid advertising on Search Engine Results Pages (SERPs). It may incorporate SEO as well.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</strong>: The aim of SEO is to use such keywords that appear first when someone searches for it.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Content Marketing</strong>: Content marketing is the art of boosting the sales simply by writing the engaging content about the product or service on website, blog, article, social media posts etc.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Influencer Marketing</strong>: Influencer content may be framed as testimonial advertising, by critics and/or stake-holders.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Campaign Marketing</strong>: It is used in branding, especially when a super-important new product is launched, to make it most awaited in the business, which gives back huge profits.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>E-Commerce Marketing</strong>: Ecommerce marketing swells sales by raising awareness about an online store and the products it is offering.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Social Media Marketing and Social Media Optimization</strong>: SMM and SMO rely on the optimum use of many social media channels, like Facebook, twitter, Instagram, Pinterest, blog, RSS feed etc. for marketing. Initial content and constant feeds are enhanced by images, videos, tag-lines etc. to catch the eye of the customer.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Direct E-Mail Marketing</strong>: In Direct email marketing, standalone advertisements are sent to a targeted list of recipients.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Display Advertising</strong>: Also known as Online Banner Advertising, it includes creation of a window for the advertisements (banner or poster form) to be seen and noticed by the consumers while going through their regular routine on internet.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Games</strong>: Paid advertisements in the starting of a new level of game or getting rewards upon watching an advertisement video in the game works as a powerful marketing tool.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Pay Per Click Advertising (PPC)</strong>: PPCs are the advertisements that appear at the top of the search engine pages when you search for the same topic.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Online Public Relations</strong>: OPR refers to the management of the relations between the organization, stake-holders and its customers using various internet marketing channels.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Online Reputation Management (ORM)</strong>: ORM is mainly involved with managing the results on websites that make endorsements and referrals on the basis of the product and services offered by a company.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Affiliate Marketing</strong>: In this type of marketing, the sales-person, or &lsquo;the affiliate&rsquo; gets rewards for his own efforts in getting maximum business for the company.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Viral Content Campaigns</strong>: This includes creating campaigns through which extraordinary content or post, which is not usually picked up by general media, but gets exponential popularity on internet.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Conversion Rate Optimization (CRO)</strong>: It is the approach of increasing the visitors to the company website which will eventually convert into the customers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>2. <strong>Non-Internet Marketing Channels</strong>: that do not need internet to provide digital media.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>E&ndash;Books</strong>: This includes white papers, videos, infographics or self-published e-books that are free to download and to be used for marketing.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Optical Disks</strong>: ACDs, VCDs and DVDs are efficient tools for getting all the relevant information in one place, from a reliable source.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>SMS</strong>: SMS is a very potent means of communication and marketing as well. It is short, crisp and provides all the required information to the receiver.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>MMS</strong>: SMS, when upgraded with an image, audio or video clip, it becomes MMS. It is short and crisp and precise as SMS, but includes the appeal of invitation that a multimedia file exhibits.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Callback and on-hold ring tones</strong>: Call back and on-hold ringtones are usually catchy, informative, yet entertaining, and many companies see them as potential reachers to random people calling their companies.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the world of marketing, every little business has competitors and hence, it is important that digital marketing strategies should be such that they reach to the largest chunk of the population. That&rsquo;s what you choose us for&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are a team of skilled, hard working, goal oriented individuals that manages your website, creates fresh and innovative content, boost your social media posts and give the opportune exposure to your DMC to bring your business into limelight.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have provided Digital Marketing Solutions, like Social Media Marketing, Facebook Application, Twitter, YouTube Videos, to some of the well-known brands, such as, <strong>Maruti A-Star, Coollip, Maruti Estilo, Tresmode, True Value and so on...</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We go beyond the commonplace digital marketing strategies and furnish well thought-out, proficient, yet innovative gimmick keeping a keen eye to the details. We give a new dimension to your Digital Marketing Campaign (DMC) and create a niche for your customers to connect with you, so that they come back every time. We increase your online visibility, create brand value, develop loyalty and trust among the consumers, overall, manage your online reputation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Doors Studio - India &amp; UAE Presence</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a leading Digital marketing Agency in Delhi,India our clientele is spread across India &amp; UAE. You can now avail our best <a href=\"digital-marketing-agency-in-uae-abudhabi-ras-al-khaimah-dubai-sharjah.php\">digital marketing services in Abudhabi, RAS-Al-kaimah, Dubai, Sharjah and UAE</a></p>', 'HIGH PERFORMANCE DIGITAL MARKETING AGENCY IN DELHI & GOA TO COVER ALL DIGITAL CHANNELS', NULL, 'TOP DIGITAL MARKETING AGENCY IN GOA, DELHI, INDIA - BUILDING BRANDS DIGITALLY', 'Online Advertising Agency & Digital Marketing Agency in Delhi, Goa - Doors Studio', 'Digital Marketing Agency and Online Advertising Agency - Doors Studio is among the top class digital Marketing Agency in Delhi and Goa that helping businesses to increase ROI and their online visibilities.', 'digital marketing company in India, digital marketing company in Delhi, digital marketing agency in India, online marketing company India', '1588254047.jpg', '2020-04-30 13:40:47', '2020-04-30 13:40:47'),
(17, 'Social Media Marketing', 'social-media-marketing', '<p class=\"text-center\"><em>More than posting, it is a Game of Thrones finale every day! </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Would you like to improve your social media marketing techniques to get maximum users?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Digital Marketing is the fastest and the most far reaching on Social media as almost half of our generation today is available &lsquo;Online!&rsquo; Doors Studio believes that Social Media Marketing is an integral part of the process of marketing your business especially when it is just in its early stages of formation. It is one the many strategic tools for your business model, its implementation, and its administration and helps define the nature of the kind of product or service you are planning to trade on this platform. For this kind of marketing the market persons need to make use of &lsquo;user generated content&rsquo; which is earned rather than media which is paid when they are think on using Social Media Marketing for driving users to their website</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Grow up your business through various social media channels such as Facebook, Twitter, G+, Linkedin, Instagram etc</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Social Media Marketing involves the users with your business and facilitates interaction on a much more private or personal level as compared to advertising or outbound marketing. This way you can use the assistance of social media platforms like Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Google+ to alleviate your business to another level altogether since the user is a much frequent user of Social media hubs stated above.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Networking is the name of game when you decide to take the way of Social Media Marketing as it gives you the facility to engage users in a lighthearted manner. It is by &lsquo;word of mouth&rsquo; that your business gets its visibility as whenever someone likes your post, blog or any product promotion they share it on their timeline or &lsquo;retweet&rsquo; or &lsquo;repost&rsquo; it. By doing this your company content appears on the wall of other people who are associated with the user who shared or liked your post, thus increasing engagement and reach which cannot be achieved through physical advertising.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Through Social Media Marketing you inculcate loyalty and following among your customers, who when they decide to follow you on social networking sites as there is a level of personal involvement with the brand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Doors Studio we generate some innovative and thought provoking ideas that you can use for the purpose of Social Media Marketing. You can completely rely on our team of experts to guide you across the Social Media Marketing frontier to enhance your business opportunity and tap maximum benefit from it.</p>', 'SMO & BRANDING SERVICES', 'SOCIAL MEDIA MARKETING COMPANY, SOCIAL MEDIA AGENCY IN DELHI & GOA', 'DOORS STUDIO - THE BEST SMO COMPANY / AGENCY IS HERE FOR BUILDING YOUR BRAND', 'Social Media Marketing Company, Social Media Agency in Delhi, Goa - Doors Studio', 'SMO Agency, Social Media Marketing Company in Delhi & Goa | India– Doors Studio is a leading India\'s best SMO Agency, social media agency, SMO Services company in Delhi, Goa, India that provides you with quality services by social media marketing to boost your brand.', 'Best SMO Services, Social Media Optimization Company India, Best SMO Services Company, Best SMO Services Company in India', '1588255447.jpg', '2020-04-30 14:04:07', '2020-04-30 14:04:07'),
(18, 'Pay Per Click Advertising', 'pay-per-click-advertising', '<p class=\"text-center\"><em>The right amount will take you to heaven, or even higher </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pay per click marketing is another great way to advertise your product or services to the viewers very efficiently. Since it comes up only when a person searches something in same category, it pin points the targeted audience who are, essentially, prospective buyers. Hence, every click becomes meaningful, unlike the click of organic traffic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As the name suggests, the Pay per Click is a paid option for the brands that are willing to pay for the sponsored ads placed at the top of a Google search page. When you choose pay per click option, your advertisement is perceived as more credible and your brand, more reliable. This increases the interest of the customer, and each time one of such advertisements is clicked, the advertiser pays small fees to the search engine, which is little price to pay to have a targeted audience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>PPC has many benefits for its users:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Being more reliable, it attracts more people.</li>\r\n	<li>Targeting right people at right time becomes effortless.</li>\r\n	<li>Advertisements can be targeted at global level or a local level, according to the regions, countries, or cities. Users can also set a distance radius for their advertisement.</li>\r\n	<li>Payments are made only for the click, which ensures that the user is paying only for the webpage visits, nothing else.</li>\r\n	<li>Since it costs very less per click, the user can begin with PPC, literally, from any amount.</li>\r\n	<li>The proportion of gaining profits by sale to paying price for ad spot is huge.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As an authorized PPC advertising agency, we avail a prospect for our clients to advertise through this paid marketing channel and make their business fly-high with great returns. There are two types of PPC, viz.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Flat Rate PPC</strong> in which you pay a fixed sum for each click, and</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Bid Based PPC</strong>, in which bidding is done among the competitors, whoever wins the bid, bags the ad spot; like, for Google advertisers, whoever has highest Google AdRank (CPC Bid multiplied by Quality Score), wins.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Both are workable options, according to your business needs and competitors. But bid-based PPC is more dynamic and new, as opposed to old and rigid Flat Rate PPC. Bid-based PPC gives an opportunity to new start-ups to put across their well-formed ads and save a lot of money if they win the spot. The key to win the bid lies with</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>targeting the customer, and</li>\r\n	<li>keyword oriented precisely drafted advertisement</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PPC is highly successful because users find the advertisements for exactly what they are searching for, and it gives an opportunity for advertisers to connect with potential customers at lowest possible prices and generate multifold sales from minimal investment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Doors Studio - India &amp; UAE Presence</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a leading PPC advertising Agency in Delhi,India our clientele is spread across India &amp; UAE. You can now avail our best <a href=\"ppc-seo-agency-company-in-uae-abudhabi-ras-al-khaimah-dubai-sharjah.php\">PPC advertising agency in Abudhabi, RAS-Al-kaimah, Dubai, Sharjah and UAE</a></p>', 'PPC ADVERTISING', 'PPC AGENCY, PAY PER CLICK ADVERTISING COMPANY, PPC MANAGEMENT IN DELHI & GOA - GENERATE QUALITY LEADS', 'TARGET THE RIGHT AUDIENCE EVERY TIME WITH PAY PER CLICK (PPC)', 'PPC Agency, Pay Per Click Advertising Company in Delhi, Goa | India - Doors Studio', 'PPC Agency, Pay Per Click Advertising Company – Doors Studio is a leading campaign management, PPC Agency, Pay Per Click Advertising and PPC management Company in Delhi, Goa, India that gives you maximum ROI for your growing business.', 'PPC Advertising Agency, PPC Advertising company, PPC campaign Management company in Delhi, PPC campaign Management company India', '1588255935.jpg', '2020-04-30 14:12:15', '2020-04-30 14:12:15'),
(19, 'Content Writing', 'content-writing', '<p class=\"text-center\"><em>Because the magic and wonders happen &lsquo;between the lines&rdquo; </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want your SEO attempt doesn&rsquo;t ultimately look like a gimmick, where getting the top rank is a fluke, you should definitely make sure that the content quality is optimal. Are you tired of trying different writers for witnessing some real established improvement in ranking? If yes, give it a final trial to us; we guarantee you won&rsquo;t have to think about the same anytime in the future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>How can our contents help your <strong>business</strong>?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Doors Studio through its immense experience understands it well on how to strategies contents for enduring results. Here we don&rsquo;t just deliver you an amusing piece of content; rather, we make sure that it addresses the SEO factor to develop your brand value.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our content service is distinguishing as it is entirely strategized as per the business dynamic of the concerned client. In addition, we ensure that adequate research is done to make the content informative enough and presented really nicely.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our content writing services include:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Copywriting</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We bring copywriting and strategic content solutions to corporates, brands, businesses, and entrepreneurs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Business content writing</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Starting from writing a business proposal to reviews, we can address all segments of business content writing</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Web content Writing</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>With our SEO optimized contents to make your site the most engaging and interactive, and thus help in improving chances of a return.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Article and Blog Writing</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We have a specialist team of article and blog content writing, those who are experienced enough to understand all aspects of these forms of writing; be it for content marketing or native site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Newsletter Writing</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We can responsibly handle your entire newsletter writing requirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Ebook Writing</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If ebook writing is part of your SEO campaign, we can bring the most of it through our specialist team of writers. Not just that we write simple stories; rather, we are experienced enough to prepare it in a platform-specific way.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Technical Writing</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Doors Studio can be the one-stop destination for your whole range of technical writing requirements. We have a specialist team for these forms of writing, those who possess hands-on experience about what they write.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Press Release</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you believe an effective PR campaign can take your business to the next level? If yes, we can prepare the perfect PR content that can meet the standard as explained above. Be it about maintaining the desired format or addressing the keyword aspects; our writers understand it well on how to make things look absolutely flawless.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So, what are you waiting for! Book your order today to take your SEO campaign to a new high.</p>', 'PROFESSIONAL CONTENT WRITING SERVICES', 'A CREATIVE CONTENT WRITING AGENCY IN DELHI & GOA', 'WE ARE COMMITTED TOWARDS DELIVERING THE MOST CREATIVE, INTUITIVE AND PRODUCTIVE CONTENT WRITING SERVICES.', 'Creative & SEO Friendly Content Writing, Copy Writing in Delhi, India - Doors Studio', 'Doors Studio is a professional content writing agency in India. As a creative content writing agency we offer creative content writing & copy writing to attracts users about your services & products which also helps in increasing your organic traffics & ROI.', 'website Design Services Company, responsive website design, custom web designs services', '1588256898.jpg', '2020-04-30 14:28:18', '2020-04-30 14:28:18'),
(20, 'SEO Content', 'seo-content', '<p>SEO content is the bow and arrow of your website arms itself with to beat the ranking on the search engine. Any and every content will not be SEO friendly by that we mean that there are certain keywords which are specific to each and every. Those same keywords act as catalysts to help to push your ranking upwards.</p>', 'SEO Content', 'SEO Content', NULL, 'SEO Content', 'SEO Content', NULL, '1583133347.jpg', '2020-03-02 07:15:47', '2020-03-02 07:15:47'),
(21, 'Paid Marketing', 'paid-marketing', '<p>Organic marketing alone can never work. Recent studies show that 70% of<br />\r\naccounts flourished only due to the healthy mix of organic and paid marketing. It<br />\r\nmight seem intimidating to your budget but it that underutilized and<br />\r\nunderestimated weapon that can reap your good results if used wisely and<br />\r\nstrategically.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nThere are two types of paid marketing you can use:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. Social Media Campaign</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Here we run advertisements or as usually called &ldquo;campaigns&rdquo; either to increase<br />\r\nbrand awareness or lead generation. The use of quirky one-liners that are a part<br />\r\nof copywriting is involved to make these campaigns a success. Here target<br />\r\naudience and other factors of demographics also play a significant role. That<br />\r\ndecides which type of audience, of what age and income group would this ad will<br />\r\nreach to part from the audience already built.<br />\r\nThe campaigns are run on all relevant social media platforms where the brand is<br />\r\nhaving its presence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>2. PPC</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This type of marketing is done on google wherein ads are run and the advertising<br />\r\nneeds to pay when a visitor clicks on it. Hence the full form is Pay Per Click. This is<br />\r\nto direct visitors to your brand apart from organic passageways.</p>', 'Paid Marketing', 'Paid Marketing', NULL, 'Paid Marketing', 'Paid Marketing', 'Paid Marketing', '1588260047.jpg', '2020-04-30 15:20:47', '2020-04-30 15:20:47'),
(22, 'Brand Reputation', 'brand-reputation', '<p>Brand reputation is a process like that of a mutual fund scheme you invest in. But here, the investment is on the daily basis via several marketing activities which you performed to reap good returns. Good returns is actually the reputation which you enjoy after your hard work and successful strategy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Brand Reputation is a challenging yet rewarding task if done nicely!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Always engage with your audience to maintain a relationship which makes them feel validated and allows them to perceive you as a service/product provider who they can approach.</li>\r\n	<li>Reviews are an insight which you must take with a sportsman spirit, but you have to be careful which is a genuine one and which is written to ridicule you.</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain a standard of your strategy by taking care of the content which goes to even the design of your graphic.</li>\r\n</ol>', 'Brand Reputation', 'Brand Reputation', NULL, 'Brand Reputation', 'Brand Reputation', 'Brand Reputation', '1588260470.jpg', '2020-04-30 15:27:50', '2020-04-30 15:27:50'),
(23, 'Brand positioning', 'brand-positioning', '<p>Before strategy comes to a decision which every marketeer make of where they wish to position a brand. It is a pre-definite goal a brand sets for itself to build a strategy around to attain it. To put it simply, you know how coffee tastes like, the one you like, you put exact ingredients to get it right. The same is with brand positioning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The agenda of any brand positioning statement it reach a place where the consumer wants are in sync with what the brand offers and are appreciating it in masses.</p>', 'Brand positioning', 'Brand positioning', NULL, 'Brand positioning', 'Brand positioning', 'Brand positioning', '1588260720.jpg', '2020-04-30 15:32:00', '2020-04-30 15:32:00'),
(24, 'Execution Strategy', 'execution-strategy', '<p>You have been told that your social media needs regular posting. But that is not how it works. It is an execution strategy but not an effective one. Just every dish has a different flavour which you attain opting for a different recipe, there is a different strategy for every brand when comes to social media posting that they all can never achieve with just one strategy: which is to post daily</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We give a solution to this by breaking this myth first and providing you with solution which is far different from the norm of regular posting. Execution strategies are different for every brand and we help you reach there.</p>', 'Execution Strategy', 'Execution Strategy', NULL, 'Execution Strategy', 'Execution Strategy', 'Execution Strategy', '1588260877.jpg', '2020-04-30 15:34:37', '2020-04-30 15:34:37');

